The dew point at the accident site was 6 degrees Celsius.
There was no obscuration at the accident site.
There was no precipitation at the accident site.
The departure point was Cape Girardeau, Missouri.
Cape Girardeau's airport code is KCGI.
No flight plan was filed for the flight.
The destination was Ankeny, Iowa.
Ankeny's airport code is KIKV.
